{"tid":594940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛津研究：倘加息一厘 本港私人債務或陷險境","createTime":"2018-03-16T09:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T10:33:07.000Z","uid":42921,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e94efaef37060cd74f5dd4491ef58f992598dd52","tid":594940,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"據牛津經濟研究院調查指，倘借貸成本上升，香港、瑞典、中國內地及澳洲的私人領域債務或陷入險境，主因該等經濟體與經濟產出相關的浮息債比例特別高。該研究涵蓋16個經濟體，指倘利率上升，家庭和企業均可能受到擠壓。<br />\n<br />\n該研究院估算，倘加息100點子，將致一年後本港利息開支增加幅度相當於其GDP的2.5%左右；其次瑞典、內地和澳洲的增幅則將相當於其GDP介乎1.5%至1.7%。(da/t)~<br />\n<br />\n阿思達克財經新聞<br />\n網址: <a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com&d=uvnUwBOD0%2FcZEeC6XjBEZMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=352d4035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com</a>"},{"pid":"28e510f9cea56a4d6ecbd750c60f1b37b5839ef3","tid":594940,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:10:20.000Z","msg":"小心比哲學撚咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d23f332c4da1442f0fd310d172ebb128adbdbd0","tid":594940,"uid":42921,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:10:48.000Z","msg":"外國班白痴仔成日用外國情況黎估香港，香港人大班錢，加一厘就有風險，笑死人"},{"pid":"9c0cc2a8f9d56e6588f18d5ac2d91b2c9b7dd806","tid":594940,"uid":158613,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9d23f332c4da1442f0fd310d172ebb128adbdbd0","tid":594940,"uid":42921,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:10:48.000Z","msg":"外國班白痴仔成日用外國情況黎估香港，香港人大班錢，加一厘就有風險，笑死人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T09:15:40.000Z","msg":"加10厘都無問題<br />\n個個full paid"},{"pid":"a847f55b381642e9e052d6d7d095ba312d12ae48","tid":594940,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c0cc2a8f9d56e6588f18d5ac2d91b2c9b7dd806","tid":594940,"uid":